  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package was signed on 2026-03-01 and subsequently updated post-signing to incorporate a supplemental mesh-refinement validation result dated 2026-03-22; the package was not re-signed after that update, introducing a future-dated evidence item relative to the recorded signatureTimestamp.",
